title: Halstead's Grossman on Opportunities in NY Real Estate (Audio)

description:
(Bloomberg) -- Taking Stock with Kathleen Hays and Pimm Fox. GUEST: Richard Grossman, President of Halstead Property, on the impact to NY residential real estate as the Fed gears up for an interest rate increase, and opportunities for investment.
